@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Crear evento OrderCreated
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "EVT-001",
  "eventType": "OrderCreated",
  "version": "1.0",
  "occurredAt": "2026-06-01T10:00:00Z",
  "producer": "order-service",
  "correlationId": "corr-001",
  "payload": {
    "userId": "USR-01",
    "orderId": "ORD-1001",
    "totalAmount": 49990,
    "currency": "CLP"
  }
}

### Listar notificaciones por usuario
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?userId=USR-01&page=1&size=10

### Consultar stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/stats

### Marcar como leida
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notifications/NOTIF-0001/read

### Registrar subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USR-01",
  "platform": "web",
  "subscription": {
    "endpoint": "https://push.example.test/subscription",
    "keys": {
      "p256dh": "demo-key",
      "auth": "demo-auth"
    }
  }
}
